O(4) NLSM with precisely $\\Theta = \\pi$ is a stable $(2+1)d$ conformal\nfield theory (CFT) with gapless bosonic modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2015 20:15:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2016 01:15:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-09"}
