ot depend on the\nbehaviour of kpc-scale structures. The superlinear ionisations significantly\nincrease the median halo mass scale for ionising photon output to >10^10 Mo,\ngiving greater hope for detecting most of ionising sources with next-generation\nfacilities. These results highlight the importance of more accurately treating\nionising sources and recombinations for modeling reionisation and its 21cm\nsignal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2015 20:16:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Feb 2016 12:10:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-08"}
