ch\nphysics of the ESO137-001 tail, future work is needed to address the importance\nof other mechanisms, such as thermal conduction and magneto hydrodynamic waves,\nin powering the emission in the tail.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2015 20:16:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Jan 2016 09:34:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-22"}
