onnections coefficients and show\nhow this rook theory model can give combinatorial explanations for many of the\nproperties of these coefficients.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2015 20:54:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Nov 2015 04:40:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2016 19:31:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-01"}
