he class, after RX J0524+4244\n(\"Paloma\", P_spin~2.3 hr). Although we cannot unambiguously establish the true\norbital period with these observations, RX J2015.6+3711 appears to be a key\nsystem in the evolution of magnetic CVs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Oct 2015 07:42:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Nov 2015 12:23:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
