e (i.e. the\nemission height variation, or the time-dependent activity across the radio\nbeam) is not easily explained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Oct 2015 12:02:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-18"}
